<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Keybay Rails example</title>
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: dark; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; }
      body { margin: 0; min-height: 100vh; display: grid; place-items: center; background: #101114; color: #f5f7ff; }
      main { width: min(680px, calc(100% - 48px)); }
      h1 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
      p { color: #b8bdcc; line-height: 1.5; }
      dl { margin: 28px 0; }
      dt { margin-top: 16px; color: #b8bdcc; font-size: 0.85rem; }
      dd { margin: 6px 0 0; padding: 20px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; border-radius: 12px; background: #20222a; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; color: #fff; }
      .warning { color: #ff8f8f; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Keybay Rails example</h1>
      <p>These values reached the running Rails process through its environment.</p>
      <dl>
        <dt>Payments API URL</dt>
        <dd><%= @payments_api_url %></dd>
        <dt>Stripe secret key</dt>
        <dd data-testid="stripe-secret-key"><%= @stripe_secret_key %></dd>
      </dl>
      <p class="warning">Demo only — never use a production credential here.</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
